name: RainySunny Umbrella Factory
overview:
RainySunny is an umbrella manufacture from China, who is professional in supplying and producing umbrellas including advertising umbrella, baby stroller umbrella, children umbrella, beach chair umbrella, car umbrella, lady’s umbrella etc.

As an experience company in umbrella field, RainySunny not only supply the correct umbrella, but also in high quality, in-time delivery, closed cooperation to its cooperators around the world. Rainysunny establish a closed umbrella supplying chain with its suppliers of fabric, plastic, steel, frame and related components, they united together and improved efficiency of their supplying action. Which is help its cooperators and customer from the world wide to reduce their cost, improve their leading time, and keep the quality in high level.

RainySunny is also introducing another solution for who is wanting not large quantity, but in high quality advertising umbrella and gift umbrella. Only if the quantity is upto 500pcs, they can order from RainySunny for promotion. Now, RainySunny is being a closed partner of worldwide buyers, purchasers and cooperators.
